snippet.textDisplay: Absolutely disgusting reporting, total hypocracy, after decades of sanctions, restricting medicines freely available to everyone, the same sanctions that caused the death of half a million Iraqi infants at the hands of America. Obviously edited dialogue by the doctor, not a mention of sanctions, which incidentally have resulted in famines across this country previously.
